Package org.jsweet.transpiler.extension

Class RemoveJavaDependenciesAdapter

java.lang.Object
org.jsweet.transpiler.extension.PrinterAdapter
org.jsweet.transpiler.extension.Java2TypeScriptAdapter
org.jsweet.transpiler.extension.RemoveJavaDependenciesAdapter
Direct Known Subclasses:
RemoveJavaDependenciesES6Adapter
public class RemoveJavaDependenciesAdapter extends Java2TypeScriptAdapter
An adapter that removes many uses of Java APIs and replace them with JavaScript equivalent when possible.
Author:
Renaud Pawlak
